07:27.011 --> 07:28.273
-WHAT'S HE GOT AGAINST MANNY?

07:28.926 --> 07:30.754
-SEE THAT CUTE GIRL OVER THERE?
-YEAH.

07:31.320 --> 07:34.932
-BRYCE USED TO GO OUT WITH HER
UNTIL SHE DISCOVERED MANNY.

07:35.063 --> 07:37.848
-THEY'RE LOOKING MORE AND MORE
LIKE REAL LIFEGUARDS EVERY DAY.

07:37.979 --> 07:40.111
-AND I SUPPOSE ALL
THREE ARE SIGNED UP

07:40.242 --> 07:41.635
FOR THE TRIP THIS WEEKEND.

07:41.765 --> 07:43.375
-I HOPE MITCH IS STILL COMING.

07:43.506 --> 07:44.725
-ARE YOU KIDDING?

07:44.855 --> 07:46.596
TWO AND A HALF DAYS
WITH A BUNCH OF

07:46.727 --> 07:49.338
HORMONE CRAZED TEENAGERS, HE
WOULDN'T MISS IT FOR THE WORLD.

07:49.469 --> 07:52.776
-CODY:
HEADS UP, HEADS DOWN, GO!

07:53.516 --> 07:54.691
-THERE YOU GO,
YOU SHOULD BE FINE.

07:54.822 --> 07:55.779
