08:08.575 --> 08:10.490
-DISPATCH: 201, 295.

08:14.798 --> 08:17.279
-GO AHEAD, 295. THIS IS 201.

08:17.409 --> 08:19.194
-DISPATCH: RESPOND TO TOWER 12,
LIFEGUARD REPORTING

08:19.324 --> 08:21.413
