WHAT HAPPENED,

08:44.087 --> 08:45.612
HE SEEMS OKAY THOUGH.

08:45.742 --> 08:46.526
-THAT'S OKAY, CAROLINE,
I CAN HANDLE IT FROM HERE.

08:46.656 --> 08:47.396
GO BACK TO YOUR TOWER.

08:47.527 --> 08:48.440
-GOOD LUCK, GUYS!

08:52.009 --> 08:54.272
-OKAY, SIR, WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?
-HE'S HAVING A HEART ATTACK.

08:54.403 --> 08:55.883
-PLEASE, MA'AM,
LET THE VICTIM RESPOND.

08:56.013 --> 08:57.580
-TALK TO THEM!

08:58.625 --> 09:02.759
-WELL, I GOT THIS TEENY
LITTLE PAIN IN MY CHEST.

09:02.890 --> 09:05.327
I DON'T KNOW WHAT SHE'S
MAKING SUCH A FUSS ABOUT.

09:05.457 --> 09:07.024
-WHERE DOES IT HURT?

09:08.896 --> 09:11.072
-WHAT?
-WHERE DOES IT HURT?

09:11.202 --> 09:13.378
-OH, WELL...

09:13.509 --> 09:15.293
-SIR, I'M OVER HERE.

09:15.424 --> 09:18.253
-OH, YEAH, WELL IT
STARTS IN MY CHEST

09:18.383 --> 09:20.168
AND IT GOES UP TO MY JAW.

09:20.298 --> 09:21.517
-WHAT BROUGHT IT ON?

09:23.084 --> 09:24.694
-I THINK IT WAS
SOMETHING I ATE.

09:24.825 --> 09:26.653
-ATE, SHMATE, THAT'S
WHAT BROUGHT IT ON.

09:26.783 --> 09:28.132
RIGHT OVER THERE!

09:32.223 --> 09:34.312
-YOUR HUSBAND'S HEART RATE
HAS STABILIZED, MRS. BEEPER.

09:34.443 --> 09:36.227
WE'RE SURE HE'S NOT
IN ANY IMMEDIATE DANGER,

09:36.358 --> 09:39.361
BUT HE WILL BE GIVEN A COMPLETE
EXAMINATION AT THE HOSPITAL.

09:39.491 --> 09:41.102
-THERE SHE IS AGAIN.

09:41.232 --> 09:43.626
SHE SHOULD BE ARRESTED FOR
ATTEMPTED MANSLAUGHTER.

09:44.235 --> 09:46.760
I AM TELLING YOU, THESE
SKIMPY BATHING SUITS,

09:46.890 --> 09:48.979
IT'S NOT SAFE TO COME
TO THE BEACH ANYMORE.

09:49.110 --> 09:51.242
-PLEASE, MRS. BEEPER,
GET IN THE CAR.

09:54.594 --> 09:55.856
-SHAME ON YOU!

09:59.424 --> 10:02.427
[SIREN BLARES]

10:02.558 --> 10:04.865
-WELL, DO YOU THINK
WE SHOULD SAY SOMETHING TO HER?

10:04.995 --> 10:08.172
-OH, COME ON, YOU DON'T THINK
SHE CAUSED THE HEART ATTACK?

10:08.303 --> 10:10.348
-NO, BUT ACCORDING
TO COUNTY POLICY,

10:10.479 --> 10:12.394
THONG BIKINIS ARE
BANNED FROM THE BEACH.

10:12.524 --> 10:16.006
-TRUE, BUT TECHNICALLY,
THAT'S NOT A THONG.

10:16.137 --> 10:17.617
IT'S A BRAZILIAN BOTTOM.

10:18.792 --> 10:20.358
THE DIFFERENCE IS SUBTLE,

10:20.489 --> 10:22.491
BUT IT DOES COVER A TAD
MORE THAN YOUR BASIC THONG.

10:24.188 --> 10:26.930
-I DIDN'T REALIZE YOU WERE
SUCH AN EXPERT ON THE SUBJECT.

10:27.061 --> 10:31.282
-WELL, NEXT TIME YOU NEED
A JUDGE FOR A BIKINI CONTEST,

10:32.240 --> 10:33.545
I'M YOUR MAN.

10:37.419 --> 10:40.074
-CODY, COME ON,
YOU'RE HOGGING IT, MAN!

10:40.204 --> 10:42.163
-HEY, CAREFUL,
YOU'LL TEAR THE PAGES!

10:42.293 --> 10:44.034
