FOOLING, BACK OFF!

10:48.735 --> 10:50.867
-WHOA, YOU GOT IT IN,
YOU REALLY DID IT.

10:50.998 --> 10:53.348
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.
IT'S AWESOME.

10:53.478 --> 10:54.697
-OOH, VERY COOL.
-LOOK, LOOK, LOOK.

10:54.828 --> 10:56.220
-WHAT'S GOING ON?

10:59.006 --> 11:00.747
