-I'M NOT UPSET.

11:53.756 --> 11:56.063
-YES, YOU ARE.
-WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME?

11:56.193 --> 11:59.109
-BECAUSE
I KNEW WHAT YOU'D SAY.

